		<p>
			This was one of my first original recipes, so it has a
			sweet (pun intended) spot for me.  
			I learned that the trick to making healthy treats out
			of traditionally unhealthy recipes, such as nutella, is
			to substitute sugar for Stevia, flavouring with
			flavoured whey protein powder, cream with frozen
			banana, and whole-milk with plant-based milk.	
		</p>
